  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6768 sitting right in the heart of massive negative gamma between 6760-6770 (-40B+ each), dealers are aggressively buying this dip as they're short gamma in BREAKOUT regime. The regime flip and wall break events with -261% 1-min GEX change signals dealers just got steamrolled and are now scrambling to hedge, creating amplified selling pressure that should persist until we either break below 6750 or rally back above 6800 where positive gamma kicks in.\n\nWatch 6770 as the critical pivot - below here and dealer buying accelerates the move down toward 6750, but any bounce gets capped hard at 6800 where dealers will aggressively sell against +34B positive gamma.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect violent swings with downside bias until we clear 6800 or crash through 6750.",
